  <brief_title>Remote Magnetic Navigation For Cavotricuspid Isthmus Ablation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Controlled Study of Remote Magnetic Catheter Navigation for Cavotricuspid Isthmus Mapping and Ablation in Patients With Typical Atrial Flutter</official_title>
