  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the influence of remote magnetic catheter navigation
      on the safety and efficacy of mapping and radiofrequency ablation of the cavotricuspid
      isthmus in patients with typical atrial flutter.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
